headline.main: Clinton Foundation Releases List of Speeches That Filled Its Coffers

snippet: The Clinton Foundation, facing heavy scrutiny of its fund-raising during Hillary Rodham Clinton’s 2016 presidential campaign, released a list of paid speeches by the Clintons that generated at least $12 million.
